title: Spring Awakening
description: A gentle practice to awaken your body's natural renewal rhythms. This session helps transition from winter stagnation to spring's natural energy while maintaining deep restfulness.
principles: progressive relaxation, breath awareness, renewal intention

title: Seasonal Transition
description: Designed to help your body adjust to changing daylight patterns and seasonal shifts. This practice supports your circadian rhythm reset while guiding you into profound relaxation.
principles: body scanning, light visualization, circadian awareness

title: Refresh & Renew
description: A revitalizing practice to clear winter's heaviness from both mind and body. This session combines gentle energy activation with deep relaxation techniques.

title: New Growth Rest
description: Inspired by nature's renewal cycle, this practice nurtures the conditions for new growth in your life while maintaining deep restfulness.
principles: growth visualization, seed sankalpas, body rotation awareness

title: Clearing Space
description: A purifying practice focused on releasing accumulated tension and creating space for fresh energy and clearer thinking.
principles: mental decluttering, breath cleansing, witness consciousness

title: Dawn Renewal
description: A shorter practice designed to reset your energy with the rising sun. Perfect for morning practice to align with spring's earlier dawns.
principles: gentle awakening, light visualization, intention setting

title: Balanced Transition
description: Supports balance during seasonal change by stabilizing energy and promoting adaptability. Excellent for those sensitive to seasonal transitions.
principles: equilibrium techniques, grounding visualization, adaptability focus
